actor Customer
participant KIOSK
participant SPP
participant CLM

Customer->KIOSK :      Proceeds to the KIOSK \n  to perform self  SIM upgrade
space -2.5
KIOSK->KIOSK : Displays Self service Menu
space -2.5
Customer->KIOSK : Selects SIM swap
KIOSK->Customer: Navigate to SIM \n selection screen
space -2.5
Customer->KIOSK: Select Physical or ESIM
space -2.5
KIOSK->Customer: Prompt to enter MSISDN \n            to upgrade
Customer->KIOSK: Enter MSISDN
space -3
KIOSK->SPP: Validate MSISDN for\n 4G upgrade check
space -3
SPP->CLM: Forwards request to CLM for 4G check
space -3
CLM->SPP:Returns SIM MSISDN check result
space -3
SPP->KIOSK: Returns with availaibility\n result
space -2.5
KIOSK->SPP: Trigger OTP verification
space -2.5
SPP->Customer: Send OTP code to MSISDN
space -2.5
KIOSK->KIOSK: Display OTP screen
space -2.5
Customer->KIOSK: Enter OTP sent to MSISDN 
space -3
KIOSK->SPP: Validates OTP
space -3
SPP->ESF: Check 4G Upgrade status
space -2.5
ESF->SPP: returns 4G upgrade check result
space -2.5
SPP->KIOSK: Returns 4G upgrade status
space -2.5
KIOSK->KIOSK :    Transitions to NIN \n verification screen
KIOSK->Customer: Display NIN Form